original: Linden, Gustaf Ragnar, tandläkare, Eksjö, f. 12/5/00 i Vena, Kalmar 1., av Karl Gustaf Arvid L. o. Olga Sofia Samuelsson. G. 27 m. Karin Andræ. Barn: Gustav f. 28, Kerstin 30, Erik 32, Margareta 37. — Stud :ex. i Eksjö 19, tandl :kand. 22, tandlä’kare 24. Praktik i Eksjö sed. 24, tandl. v. Smål. sinnesslöanst. i Eksjö sed. 25. Stud:-resa t. Essen 37.
translated:
Linden, Gustaf Ragnar, dentist, Eksjö, born on May 12, 1900 in Vena, Kalmar 1st, son of Karl Gustaf Arvid L. and Olga Sofia Samuelsson. Married on the 27th with Karin Andræ. Children: Gustav born in 1928, Kerstin in 1930, Erik in 1932, and Margareta in 1937. 

Education: Examined in Eksjö in 1919, dental studies in 1922, qualified as a dentist in 1924. Practiced in Eksjö since 1924, also worked as a dentist at the Småland mental hospital in Eksjö since 1925. Study trip to Essen in 1937.
